      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      393.1,
      526.73,
      407.27
    ],
    "text": "In the case of State of U.P. vs Dr Ravindra Prakash Mittal, 1992 2 SCJ 549, it was",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
