    "bbox": [
      107.24,
      529.2,
      407.79,
      543.37
    ],
    "text": "2) The circumstances should be conclusive in nature;",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.24,
      556.92,
      530.4,
      571.09
    ],
    "text": "3) All the facts so established should be consistent with the hypothesis of",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.24,
      578.52,
      325.83,
      592.69
    ],
    "text": "guilt and inconsistent with innocence;",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.24,
      606.12,
      530.3,
      620.29
    ],
